# Lab Day 01: Governing Equations - Continuity Equation Implementation

> **Phase 01: Foundation Theory (Days 01-12)**
> **Topic:** Conservation Laws for CFD - Hands-on Implementation
> **Prerequisites:** Day 01 theory content, OpenFOAM installation

---

## Lab Overview

**Duration:** 3-4 hours
**Difficulty:** Beginner
**Type:** CFD Implementation

### Learning Objectives

By completing this lab, you will:
- **CFD:** Implement the continuity equation in OpenFOAM, understand fvm vs fvc operators, add mass source terms, verify conservation
- **C++:** Work with templates (`tmp<fvMatrix<Type>>`), operator overloading, const references

